/*
Analysis:
Suppose n<m, each vertical line of nXm matrix is the same in terms of unordered U,V pairs (u@v equals v@u)),
so the essence of convolution matrix is to construct or perform an communicative operation
on each pair composed of one element from two vectors each.
This communicative operation is chosen to be inner product. There exist other choices.
*/
